===Noun===
'''scalar product'''

#(''Mathematics'') the [[product]] of two [[vector]]s computed as the sum of the corresponding [[element]]s of the vectors, or, equivalently, as the product of the [[magnitude]]s of the vectors and the [[cosine]] of the [[angle]] between their directions.  Compare [[vector product]]

